176
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:56,190
- Come in.
- Okay.

177
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:04,230
Aren't we covering CEO Kim Moon Sik this time?

178
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:05,580
So?

179
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:09,720
