182
00:19:15,090 --> 00:19:17,590
Don't you think I should personally meet him
and ask him?

183
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:22,280
"We think something is fishy about you
because of this and that. Are we correct?" Like that.

184
00:19:22,280 --> 00:19:24,700
- That sounds right.
- The problem is

185
00:19:24,700 --> 00:19:29,710
if he would accept our request for interview.

186
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:34,000
