193
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:53,140
I understand. Then, I'll contact his side myself.

194
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:55,160
You're going to meet Kim Moon Sik?

195
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:57,080
Actually I

